text: National Tsing Hua University (NTHU; ) is a university in Taiwan. It was founded in 1911 (currently Tsing Hua University). It moved to Hsinchu City in 1955 . NTHU is one of the four universities of the University System of Taiwan. ==Nobel Prize winners== *Dr.Chen-Ning Yang (Physics) *Dr.Tsung-Dao Lee (Physics) *Dr.Yuan-Tseh Lee (Chemistry) ==Other websites== *NTHU T Category:1955 establishments in Asia Category:20th-century establishments in Taiwan
